Whereas the Louisville Cardinals have won 3 national
			 titles and appeared in 10 NCAA Final Fours, their first title and third Final
			 Four appearance under Coach Rick Pitino;

Whereas junior center Gorgui Dieng was named Big East
			 Conference Defensive Player of the Year and First Team All-Big East, along with
			 junior guard Russ Smith;

Whereas junior forward Luke Hancock was named Most
			 Outstanding Player of the 2013 NCAA Final Four, the first nonstarter to win the
			 award;

Whereas each player, coach, athletic trainer, and staff
			 member of the University of Louisville men’s basketball team dedicated their
			 season and tireless efforts to a successful team effort;
